Description: Centrally located in Saint-Lazare, Quebec, Au Naturel’s soy candles are all made with 100% non-GMO soy wax. They are hand poured and undyed soy candles in mason jars, tins and upcycled containers. All our wicks are HTP (high tensile paper), which contain no lead or chemicals. They are scented with the finest plant based oils that are phthalate free. There are no dyes in our candles to keep them as natural and pure as possible. They burn cleaner and longer than paraffin candles. Soy wax is non-toxic, so they wont release toxins into the air as they burn. At Au Naturel we are focused on providing great products and an outstanding service.  We believe everyone should have the opportunity to purchase non-toxic and healthy products. Just because they are good for you does not mean they have to cost a fortune! We strive to use as many organic, natural and renewable resources to make all our  products. Our containers are all 100% recyclable, biodegradable or reusable. We guarantee the lowest possible prices and the best possible customer service. We strive to give you a product you will enjoy from start to finish!
